com.clarionmedia.infinitum.di.impl

Class ConfigurableBeanFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clarionmedia.infinitum.di.impl.ConfigurableBeanFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeanFactory

    public class ConfigurableBeanFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements BeanFactory

    Implementation of BeanFactory for storing beans that have been configured in infinitum.cfg.xml. ConfigurableBeanFactory also acts as a service locator for InfinitumContext.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0 04/23/12
    Author:
    Tyler Treat
